					before they finally implemented it
				</li>
				<li>A bunch of ESLint rules</li>
				<li>
					Teaching people how to write their first JavaScript tool
					through talks, workshops, and a little website: <a
						href="https://astsareawesome.com/"
						target="_blank"
						>astsareawesome.com<a></a>
					</a>
